# ğŸ¨ 1. Purpose

This document defines the **Design Intelligence Engine** for Flow Studio â€”  
a universal design framework that enables AI agents (Arto, Stylist, Builder, Curator, and Maestro) to produce *any visual style, any layout, any brand system* on demand.

This is **not** a style guide.

It is the **meta-design model** â€” the cognitive framework the agents use to:
- understand style requests  
- interpret aesthetic language  
- generate design systems dynamically  
- adapt to brands, industries, and emotional contexts  
- create layouts, components, tokens, HTML/CSS  
- evaluate and refine visual output  
- learn from references (URLs, screenshots, MCP browsing)  

This foundation ensures the system can design:
- premium medical landing pages  
- luxury lifestyle brands  
- real-estate investor dashboards  
- mobile-first SaaS apps  
- ecommerce product pages  
- childrenâ€™s educational interfaces  
- high-conversion marketing funnels  
- minimalist corporate websites  
- ANYTHING the user requests  

without being locked into a fixed palette, typography scale, or style.

