- Mapping emotional tone  
- Proposing multiple style options  
- Producing wireframes and flow logic  
- Using MCP browser for reference analysis  

## 5.2 Stylist â€“ Design Polish  
Responsible for:
- Turning Artoâ€™s concept into design tokens  
- Palette creation  
- Typography pairing  
- Spatial rhythm  
- Aesthetic refinement  
- Visual consistency  
- Accessibility compliance  

## 5.3 Builder â€“ Components  
Responsible for:
