- Catching inconsistencies  
- Suggesting refinements  
- Using screenshots from Playwright MCP  

## 5.5 Maestro â€“ Orchestrator  
Responsible for:
- Running the full multi-agent workflow  
- Synchronizing Arto â†’ Stylist â†’ Builder â†’ Curator  
- Triggering refinements  
- Ensuring output meets user goals  
- Managing complexity and phases  

